              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--ultramarine);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">YLT</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">In the third month of the going out of the sons of Israel from the land of Egypt, in this day they have come into the wilderness of Sinai,</span></div>
