              <div><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--verdigris, #4a7c59);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">WEB</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">In the third month after the children of Israel had gone out of the land of Egypt, on that same day they came into the wilderness of Sinai.</span></div>
