              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--vermillion);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">ASV</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">Now therefore<S>8085</S>, if ye will obey my voice<S>6963</S> indeed<S>8085</S>, and keep<S>8104</S> my covenant<S>1285</S>, then ye shall be mine own possession<S>5459</S> from among all peoples<S>5971</S>: for all the earth is mine<S>776</S>:</span></div>
